✨ 5th Place #NeverSettlePortraits photo! ✨  Congrats @am_do! You've won a JCC+ Black T-shirt! 😱
@am_do explains how her portrait captures the Never Settle Spirit: "The man in this picture is a very inspiring person for me. I shared some of the most amazing moments of my life with him. He is always trying to go further and try new things. He doesn't care about other people opinions and just does what makes him happy. He taught me that you always have to go out of your comfort zone and never settle ... Then the magic happens! "
